"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eel\" title=\"Eel\">Eel</a> in place of Fish will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Unagi\" title=\"Unagi\">Unagi</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Carrots\" title=\"Carrots\"><img alt=\"Carrots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Carrots.png?d06e20\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili\" title=\"Spicy Chili\"><img alt=\"Spicy Chili.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spicy_Chili.png?ec866b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\"><img alt=\"Monster Meat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meat.png?9251b3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tropical_Fish\" title=\"Tropical Fish\"><img alt=\"Tropical Fish.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Tropical_Fish.png?1cde94\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Seaweed\" title=\"Roasted Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Roasted Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roasted_Seaweed.png?d034e5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili\" title=\"Spicy Chili\"><img alt=\"Spicy Chili.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spicy_Chili.png?ec866b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/64px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td><td>Adding 2 Raw Seaweed will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/California_Roll\" title=\"California Roll\">California Roll</a></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Normal_Meats\" title=\"Normal Meats\"><img alt=\"Normal Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Normal_Meats.png?9e28e2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Morsels\" title=\"Morsels\"><img alt=\"Morsels.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Morsels.png?1ecfe8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili\" title=\"Spicy Chili\"><img alt=\"Spicy Chili.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spicy_Chili.png?ec866b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili\" title=\"Spicy Chili\"><img alt=\"Spicy Chili.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spicy_Chili.png?ec866b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/64px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td><td>50% chance to result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Lasagna\" title=\"Monster Lasagna\">Monster Lasagna</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/32px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Tips</span></h2>\n<ul><li>This food is relatively cheap to make, requiring only a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Morsel\" title=\"Morsel\">Morsel</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\">Monster Meat</a>, and two farm vegetables. It is also quick to prepare in a Crock Pot, requiring 10 seconds of cooking time. If one can manage to preserve vegetables long enough or find them quickly, this food can be particularly useful during <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Winter\">Winter</a> as it increases perceived temperature.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Spicy_Chili_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Spicy_Chili_128x128.png/120px-Spicy_Chili_128x128.png?3adc6f\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spicy_Chili#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
